data.description: Discover your opportunity in this sprawling Yukon property, boasting 2.5 acres of land with a mobile home and a workshop. While the mobile home requires remodeling to secure financing, its livable condition makes it a perfect project for a handyman or someone eager to customize their space. Sold in "as is" condition for cash only, the true value lies in the acreage, workshop, and existing well and utilities. Ideal for those seeking a prime lot with existing infrastructure, ripe for a flip or new mobile home. Priced competitively based on area comparables, seize this chance and bring forth your offer today!
